products.name: Suede Vegan Leather Moto Jacket
products.description: Classic asymmetrical moto jacket in a rich tan vegan suede. Features silver-tone hardware, notched lapels with snaps, and functional zip pockets.

products.name: Geometric Patchwork Corduroy Shacket
products.description: Cropped corduroy jacket featuring a unique split design with a neutral-toned geometric tribal pattern on one side. Finished with dropped shoulders and metallic buttons.

products.name: Chunky Pearl-Button Cable Cardigan
products.description: Cream-colored oversized cardigan with heavy cable knit detailing and decorative pearl-style buttons. Soft V-neckline and balloon sleeves for a cozy silhouette.

products.name: Heritage Oversized Graphic Cardigan
products.description: Vintage-inspired oversized cardigan in charcoal and grey knit. Features a complex abstract heritage pattern, dropped shoulders, and contrast ribbing.

products.name: Wildflower Embroidered Hoodie
products.description: Oatmeal-toned heavy fleece hoodie featuring delicate multi-colored floral embroidery across the shoulder and chest. High-quality needlework with purple and pink accents.

products.name: Fair Isle Sweater & Denim Overall Set
products.description: A curated two-piece look featuring a mustard-tone Fair Isle knit sweater paired with high-waisted black denim overall shorts with silver button hardware.

products.name: Tasseled Peplum Boho Blouse
products.description: Lightweight linen-blend tunic with a gathered peplum waist and geometric embroidery along the yoke. Features a self-tie tassel neckline and elasticated cuffs.

products.name: Bell-Sleeve Floral Linen Tunic
products.description: Sage green linen blouse with a deep V-neckline framed by purple rose embroidery. Features dramatic tiered bell sleeves and a drawstring tassel waist.
